# Quotation Workflow - User Guide

## Quick Start

Generate PowerPoint and PDF from verified proposal templates with a single command.

```bash
/quotation generate slide <template.md>
```

## What It Does

Converts verified proposal templates (markdown) into:
- **PowerPoint presentation** (.pptx) with viAct branding
- **PDF document** (.pdf) ready to send to clients

## Requirements

### Input
- ✅ Verified proposal template (`.md` format)
- ✅ No placeholders (no `[PLACEHOLDER_ID]` tags)
- ✅ 12 sections following viAct proposal structure

### Dependencies (Auto-Checked)
- ✅ pptx skill (`~/.claude/skills/pptx/`)
- ✅ pdf skill (`~/.claude/skills/pdf/`)
- ✅ LibreOffice (for PDF generation)

## Usage

### Basic Command

```bash
/quotation generate slide Leda_Inio_template.md
```

